            "body": "Hey there, \n\nAna from Theneo. Theneo is a tool for generating Stripe-like API Docs. Using AI, we are the first company to automate the full life cycle of documentation, from generating content to publishing. Theneo was built with the belief that generating high-quality, interactive documentation should not be tedious and we provide the tool to do just that. Theneo is used in production by more than 3000 companies\n\nUsing Theneo you can: \n\n* Build interactive API docs\n* Taylor your documentation\n* Update docs automatically (via IDE extensions and github integration)\n* Built for everyone \n* Bring all of your docs together with the Developer Portal\n* Let your users test APIs using the API Explorer\n\nHere is a quick video of how it all works\n\n<a href=\"https://www.loom.com/share/792fc6008a914d068ff8b34994fbc467\">\n    <p>Theneo - Quick Guide how it works - Watch Video</p>\n    <img style=\"max-width:300px;\" src=\"https://cdn.loom.com/sessions/thumbnails/792fc6008a914d068ff8b34994fbc467-with-play.gif\">\n  </a>\n\n\nSome of the APIs and Developer Portals generate in Theneo\n* https://app.theneo.io/pleo/docs\n* https://app.theneo.io/tbc/docs \n* https://docs.waivr.co/\n* https://docs.ditchcarbon.com/\n* https://www.meight.com/api/docs \n\nFor Startup Community \n",
