            "title": "Ultimate Tournament 🕹 Compete in Online Games for Real Cash",
            "body": "**What We Do**\n\nThe Ultimate Arcade allows players to compete against each other in competitive games for real money. We also offer 3rd party integrations so game developers can list their games on our site and generate revenue through a brand new monetization channel.\n\n**What Problems are we Solving**\n\n* Low burnout games with cash prizes for gamers who want to play and earn money competitively\n* Quick to learn alternatives for gamblers who can’t legally gamble online in their state or are looking for new action\n* Unique monetization channels for game developers and content creators\n\nUltimate Arcade offers a brand new avenue of entertainment to gamblers looking to get more action but in a way that puts them in control of the outcome. Skill-based gaming is also far less regulated than traditional gambling and appeals to audiences where traditional online gambling is not permitted, but skill-based games are totally ok!\n\nOur third-party development program opens up a new channel for game developers to monetize their games that are not through advertising or direct game sales. Competitive play can generate far more revenue than traditional advertising channels and allows players to engage with content in a brand new way.\n\n**Want to Get Involved?** \n\nGreat! We would love to have you!\n\n_Investors_\n\nPlease shoot us an email → [**founders@ultimatetournament.io**](mailto:founders@ultimatetournament.io)\n\n_Game Developers / Content Creators / Other Inquiries_\n\nPlease shoot us an email → [**support@ultimatetournament.io**](mailto:support@ultimatetournament.io)\n\n_Want to play and be a part of our fantastic community?_\\\nJoin here → [**https://discord.gg/3kntK6RXAU**](https://discord.gg/3kntK6RXAU)\n\n**Check us out at** → <https://ultimatearcade.io>",
