            "title": "Cambio- Fix bad credit, build good credit ",
            "body": "[Cambio](https://www.cambiomoney.com) makes financial rebuilding simple and affordable for the 65 million consumers with a credit score below 650.\n\n**The problem:**\n\n* Having an item in collections can keep your credit score below 650 for 7 years\n* It’s a 2-4 year complex process to get these items resolved and to show positive credit history\n* Consumers spend an extra $1,500 annually on credit repair services\n\n**Introducing Cambio:**\n\nOur platform helps consumers address the 3 most important tasks to rebuild their finances.\n\n* Fix: we do a soft pull of our members credit, automatically identify and fix hurtful items on their credit reports 🛠️\n* Build: Members can qualify for a 0% loan, and each payment is reported to the credit bureaus. At the end of the loan, their paid down balance is available in a savings account 🚀\n* Save: refinance high-interest auto loans through an alternative decisioning model 🚗\n\n![uploaded image](/media/?type=post&id=64180&key=user_uploads/796542/3003cf96-7f2b-47b9-accc-1210ad3a26dd)\n\n### **7 in 10 members see a credit score improvement in the first 30 days, by an average of 32 points.**\n\n**Why we built Cambio:**\n\nIn 2014, I co-founded SavvyIntel, we bootstrapped and I went into debt to keep the business afloat.  In 6 months, I went from having a 780+ credit score to going into collections and having my credit score drop into the 570s.  SavvyIntel got acquired in 2017, it still took me 4 years to rebuild my credit back to 780. We know the pain and want to make it easier for consumers to get ahead financially.\n\n**Our ask from the YC community:**\n\n* **Partnerships:** We are seeking partnerships with community-based organizations, non-profits and influencers.\n* **Auto refi program**: We are launching an auto refinance program, and are seeking capital debt investment partners.  We’ve received commitments from banks and credit unions and are looking for additional partners.\n\nIf you’ve got recommendations, please send them to [founders@cambiomoney.com](mailto:founders@cambiomoney.com)",
