            "id": 64261,
            "title": "Sunlight🔆- Plaid for the Creator Economy",
            "body": "Guy, Gil and I are thrilled to introduce [Sunlight](https://www.sunlightapi.com/) to unlock the untapped potential of FinTechs in the Creator Economy! \\\n\\\n**The Problem:**\n\nCreators have a unique and completely unprecedented financial profile in the history of the world economy: their income takes many forms and is usually spread out across dozens of platforms. Getting a clear picture of a creator’s legitimacy, financial stability and overall potential is a challenge for many service providers in finance, insurance, marketing and other sectors.\n\n\\\n**The Solution:**\n\nThat’s why we created Sunlight: a single, universal API allowing businesses to connect to a creator’s account on every platform. With the creator’s consent, service providers can get immediate and continuous access to a wide range of data, giving them full visibility into the health of a creator’s business.\n\nWith its read/write capabilities, the Sunlight API supports many use cases across industries:\n\n\\\n**Know Your Creator (KYC) -** Sunlight allows you to verify in just one click that your creators are who they say they are, and actually own the accounts and online assets they’re claiming to own.\n\n\\\n**Direct Deposit Switching -** For banking solutions, Sunlight allows creators to switch their direct deposit to your bank account, across all platforms, with the tap of a button.\n\n\\\n**Income & Performance Verification -** Get direct and continuous access to comprehensive income and performance data from multiple platforms – with the user’s consent – to properly underwrite creators and unlock a new wave of financial services designed for creators.\n\n\\\n**Our Ask**\n\nIf you’re building for the Creator Economy or need universal programmable access to creator platforms, email [founders@sunlightapi.com](https://mailto:founders@sunlightapi.com) to skip the waiting list and start using our API!\\\n\\\nCheck out our website: [sunlightapi.com](https://www.sunlightapi.com/)\n\n🚀☀️",
