            "id": 64252,
            "title": "Segna ✨ - The best way to let your users import data files",
            "body": "### 🤔 **Problem**\n\nImporting csv files (or other tabular files) is a drag on your customers' user experience and a frustration for product and tech teams.\\\nNo user enjoys downloading example spreadsheets, populating them, and uploading them only to have them fail because the data isn’t in the exact structure and format that you required.\n\nIf this sounds familiar, or if you upload files into your platform, you should be using Segna!\n\n### **🔥 How Segna solves it**\n\nSegna provides an end-to-end solution to your data importer workflow.\\\nWe automatically normalize and clean your data and allow you to customize your data importing workflow. Use our API directly from your frontend and/or backend, or use our prebuilt UI components for a low-code experience with maximum flexibility.\n\nHere’s what Segna does:\n\n1. Smart data detection and parsing - don’t worry if there is junk surrounding data; we will automatically detect where the table is located in the csv\n\n   ![uploaded image](/media/?key=user_uploads/489739/2dbfdd62-f8fd-43a1-ad9c-2ec2357512ab)\n\n2. Automatically matches/renames input columns to the desired schema - even if they don’t match exactly\n\n   ![uploaded image](/media/?key=user_uploads/489739/cd751ef5-6083-4cc8-a64e-439880e66a6f)\n\n3. Automatic datetime formatting\n4. Identifies missing rows and inconsistent formatting, and fixes them\n5. You have complete visibility of your data - see if your data makes sense. You have access to metrics and metadata to any file uploaded, such as:\n   1. Number of missing values\n   2. Data type of each column\n   3. Identified timezone of datetime columns\n   4. Unique values in the dataset\n   5. And much more!\n\n      ![uploaded image](/media/?key=user_uploads/489739/0c56c7a6-ad4e-4f8f-9ab5-6e7bcfa0e11a)\n\n\n### **🤝 Give us a try!**\n\n**Try:** Go to <http://platform.segna.io> and get started today. No demos. No credit cards. 14-day free trial.\n\n**We need your help!** We want to speak with companies that:\n\n1. Allow users to upload files during customer onboarding\n2. Routinely upload tabular files into their products - this might be price books, inventory, etc.\n3. Have already implemented a solution or are using a competitor - we’d love to hear about your experience.\n\nIf this describes your company, your previous company, or someone you know, we would love to connect and see how we can help. **Please reach out to us at** [**founders@segna.io**](mailto:founders@segna.io)",
